				<div class="width_70 right mob_full_width">
					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center">Your photograph can be mounted in a frame such as the one shown in the video above for a small extra cost. Our frames are simple, elegant and match most decors, and they come in either black or white. They can be hung on the wall, or stood up using
