				<div class="width_70 right mob_full_width">
					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center">A monogram is an emblem featuring a name and a date and it's perfect for anniversaries or birthdays. It makes your photograph even more special and personalised. Here are some examples:</p>

					<div class="width_40 padding_bottom_large mob_full_width" style="display:inline-block"><img src="/images/silver/alice.svg" style="width:200px;"></div>
					<div class="width_40  padding_bottom_large mob_full_width" style="display:inline-block"><img src="/images/silver/georgina.svg" style="width:100px;"></div>

