				<div class="width_30 left centred mob_full_width">
					<img src="/images/silver/camera.svg" class="w80px padding_top_large" />
				</div>


				<div class="width_70 right mob_full_width">
					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center">Now the hard bit: choosing which photograph to use! You can upload a photo now, email a photo later or if you have an older photo that you'd like us to scan, you can post it to us too. </p>

					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_top_small padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center slant">Due to the silver foiling process we will convert all images to black and white first and retouch them where appropriate to get you the most impressive results.</p>

					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_top_small padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center">We'll send you a digital preview before printing so you can check everything is perfect, and if you need any advice we're here to help.</p>

					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_top_small padding_bottom_large mob_text_center slant">Remember, you don't have to upload a photo now: you can skip this option and upload it later, or email it to us at <a href="mailto:david@casamiento.co.uk" class="bottom_dotted">david@casamiento.co.uk</a>, or even on messenger via our <a href="http://www.facebook.com/dreamsonpaper2016"
						 class="bottom_dotted">Facebook page</a>. You'll receive extra instructions when you've placed your order.</p>

