						<li>If you approve everything before 5pm on a Monday, your order will arrive on Friday</li>
						<li class="padding_top_small"> If you approve everything before 5pm on a Friday, your order will arrive the next Friday</li>
						<li class="padding_top_small">If you approve everything before 5pm on a Wednesday, your order will arrive the following Tuesday</li>
					</ul>

					<p class="tight_line_spacing  mob_text_center">We can post to you, or direct to the recipient of your gift. All our photos are wrapped and presented beautifully: they don't come in boring brown jiffy bags. </p>


					<p class="tight_line_spacing padding_bottom_medium mob_text_center slant">If you need something quickly, we can offer express delivery, which means we will post your photo the next working day after you've approved the preview. So if you approve before 5pm on a Monday, you'll receive it on the Wednesday. </p>

